kizai
=====

a minimal static site generator.

usage
-----

    kizai build

builds the current project.

    kizai serve

serves the current project.

structure
---------

    .
    ├── meta.yml
    ├── static/
    ├── posts/
    ├── pages/
    └── template/

- `meta.yml`: site metadata
- `static/`: static assets
- `posts/`: blog posts
- `pages/`: static pages
- `template/`: html templates

features
--------

- markdown support
- syntax highlighting
- RSS feed generation
- photo galleries
- automatic post sorting by date
- development server with live reload

license
-------

